ta-v-02330e3a>caption</span><span class="token attr-value" data-v-02330e3a><span class="token punctuation" data-v-02330e3a>=</span><span class="token punctuation" data-v-02330e3a>&quot;</span>RmList<span class="token punctuation" data-v-02330e3a>&quot;</span></span> <span class="token attr-name" data-v-02330e3a>:items</span><span class="token attr-value" data-v-02330e3a><span class="token punctuation" data-v-02330e3a>=</span><span class="token punctuation" data-v-02330e3a>&quot;</span>items<span class="token punctuation" data-v-02330e3a>&quot;</span></span><span class="token punctuation" data-v-02330e3a>&gt;</span></span><span class="token tag" data-v-02330e3a><span class="token tag" data-v-02330e3a><span class="token punctuation" data-v-02330e3a>&lt;/</span>rm-list</span><span class="token punctuation" data-v-02330e3a>&gt;</span></span>
</code></pre> <div class="line-numbers-wrapper" data-v-02330e3a><span class="line-number" data-v-02330e3a>1</span><br data-v-02330e3a></div></div><div class="language-js line-numbers-mode" data-v-02330e3a><pre class="language-js" data-v-02330e3a><code data-v-02330e3a><span class="token function" data-v-02330e3a>data</span><span class="token punctuation" data-v-02330e3a>(</span><span class="token punctuation" data-v-02330e3a>)</span> <span class="token punctuation" data-v-02330e3a>{</span>
  <span class="token keyword" data-v-02330e3a>return</span> <span class="token punctuation" data-v-02330e3a>{</span>
    items<span class="token operator" data-v-02330e3a>:</span> <span class="token punctuation" data-v-02330e3a>[</span><span class="token string" data-v-02330e3a>'東京'</span><span class="token punctuation" data-v-02330e3a>,</span> <span class="token string" data-v-02330e3a>'大阪'</span><span class="token punctuation" data-v-02330e3a>,</span> <span class="token string" data-v-02330e3a>'名古屋'</span><span class="token punctuation" data-v-02330e3a>,</span> <span class="token string" data-v-02330e3a>'沖縄'</span><span class="token punctuation" data-v-02330e3a>]</span><span class="token punctuation" data-v-02330e3a>,</span>
  <span class="token punctuation" data-v-02330e3a>}</span>
<span class="token punctuation" data-v-02330e3a>}</span><span class="token punctuation" data-v-02330e3a>,</span>
</code></pre> <div class="line-numbers-wrapper" data-v-02330e3a><span class="line-number" data-v-02330e3a>1</span><br data-v-02330e3a><span class="line-number" data-v-02330e3a>2</span><br data-v-02330e3a><span class="line-number" data-v-02330e3a>3</span><br data-v-02330e3a><span class="line-number" data-v-02330e3a>4</span><br data-v-02330e3a><span class="line-number" data-v-02330e3a>5</span><br data-v-02330e3a></div></div></div> <div class="preview" data-v-4470d30b data-v-02330e3a><div data-v-4470d30b></div></div> <!----></div> <p>⭐️ 配列の中にオブジェクトが入る場合</p> <div class="code-preview" data-v-02330e3a><div class="code" data-v-02330e3a><div class="language-vue line-numbers-mode" data-v-02330e3a><pre class="language-vue" data-v-02330e3a><code data-v-02330e3a><span class="token tag" data-v-02330e3a><span class="token tag" data-v-02330e3a><span class="token punctuation" data-v-02330e3a>&lt;</span>rm-list</span> <span class="token attr-name" data-v-02330e3a>com-id</span><span class="token attr-value" data-v-02330e3a><span class="token punctuation" data-v-02330e3a>=</span><span class="token punctuation" data-v-02330e3a>&quot;</span>list-demo<span class="token punctuation" data-v-02330e3a>&quot;</span></span> <span class="token attr-name" data-v-02330e3a>caption</span><span class="token attr-value" data-v-02330e3a><span class="token punctuation" data-v-02330e3a>=</span><span class="token punctuation" data-v-02330e3a>&quot;</span>RmList<span class="token punctuation" data-v-02330e3a>&quot;</span></span> <span class="token attr-name" data-v-02330e3a>:items</span><span class="token attr-value" data-v-02330e3a><span class="token punctuation" data-v-02330e3a>=</span><span class="token punctuation" data-v-02330e3a>&quot;</span>items<span class="token punctuation" data-v-02330e3a>&quot;</span></span> <span class="token attr-name" data-v-02330e3a>mode</span><span class="token attr-value" data-v-02330e3a><span class="token punctuation" data-v-02330e3a>=</span><span class="token punctuati